products.name: New Year
products.summary: Ringing in 2024!

items.label: Cheers to 2023, and we hope you have a wonderful new year in 2024! Gold 2024 balloons sit ontop of the avatar.

products.name: Rift Butterfly
products.summary: The Rift Butterfly is a type of sentient Rift that is shaped like a butterfly. This reward is exclusive to the Fortnite Quest.

items.label: A rift butterfly shines in the center of the avatar, flutters its wings, and returns to the top of the avatar.

products.name: Batarang
products.summary: The Batarang is Batman’s legendary throwing weapon, blending precision and versatility to instill fear in his enemies. This reward is exclusive to the Become the Knight Quest.

items.label: A spinning, bat-shaped metallic projectile hurtles into and impacts the screen, leaving a massive crack.

products.name: Bush Camper
products.summary: Exclusive to the Fortnite OG Quest for a limited time.

items.label: A bush encircles the avatar, with leaves gently rustling and swaying in a circular motion.

products.name: Shield Potion
products.summary: Exclusive to the Fortnite Ballistic Quest for a limited time.

items.label: A potion bottle is uncorked, its contents emptied, and a pixelated aura swipes over the avatar from bottom to top.

products.name: TGA Controller
products.summary: Exclusive to The Game Awards Quest for a limited time.

items.label: Two joysticks and keypads control a target that moves in all directions around the profile picture.

products.name: Shadow
products.summary: Exclusive to The Sonic 3 Quest for a limited time.

items.label: Shadow teleports around multiple times, leaving a red and orange trail while striking various dynamic poses.

products.name: Rec Room Lightning
products.summary: Exclusive to the Rec Room Quest for a limited time.

items.label: A streak of orange lightning surrounds the avatar.

products.name: WINGMAN'S GOT IT
products.summary: Exclusive to the VALORANT GO GET EM WINGS Quest for a limited time.

items.label: VALORANT Agent Gekko's cute yellow creature happily bounces on top of your avatar

products.name: Heart-to-Heart
products.summary: Feel the love all around.

items.label: A flurry of pink and red hearts surround around your avatar, swirling with a gentle touch before settling into a snug, cheek-to-cheek cuddle.

products.name: Jeff the Land Shark
products.summary: Exclusive to the Marvel Rivals Quest for a limited time.

items.label: Jeff the Land Shark is an absolutely adorable, chonky cartoon shark who looks like it just discovered its love for snacks and hugs. It’s rocking a stylish pink collar with a shiny gold tag, like it’s ready to be your best aquatic buddy. Its big toothy grin says, “I’m cute, but I could still chomp if needed!”.

products.name: Fuchsia Agent
products.summary: Exclusive to the Strinova Fuchsia Quest for a limited time.

items.label: A Fuchsia Agent character with a red shark swimming around the character's gray headband.

products.name: Fortnite Boogie Bomb
products.summary: Exclusive to the Fortnite OG S2 Quest for a limited time.

items.label: A Boogie Bomb explodes, lowering a disco ball causing a festive disco light show

products.name: Scout
products.summary: Exclusive to the Sid Meier's Civilization VII Quest for a limited time.

items.label: An older man wearing a green cape and gray feathered hat holds a wooden staff and looks into the distance while shielding his eyes to scout ahead. Next to him, his sitting dog companion stands up and looks in the same direction.

products.name: Hoppy Day
products.summary: Brb, out frolicking.

items.label: Your avatar has found a friend in the shape of a little brown bunny. It hops in delight when it sees you.

products.name: Afternoon Breeze
products.summary: A calm rest in the meadow.

items.label: Your avatar stands in a dreamy meadow, where pink and orange flowers sway to nature’s rhythm, sending petals twirling through the soft breeze.

products.name: Shower Stroll
products.summary: Chasing rainbows after the storm.

items.label: A soft rain drapes over your avatar, leaving a shimmering rainbow glow that whispers a touch of magic into the misty air.

products.name: Exoborne
products.summary: Exclusive to the Exoborne Wishlist Quest for a limited time.

items.label: Metallic armor surrounds the avatar with pieces shifting into place and yellow indicator lights turning on.

products.name: Big Dill Chain
products.summary: Exclusive to the Fortnite Quest for a limited time.

items.label: A gold chain holding a gold medallion with a D that has two vertical slashes through it surrounds a green cap.

products.name: Pathojen
products.summary: Exclusive to the FragPunk Launch Quest for a limited time.

items.label: This avatar decoration features a vibrant, neon-colored circular flame effect with an energetic, cartoonish character at the bottom left.

products.name: Split Avatar Decoration
products.summary: Exclusive to the Split Fiction Quest for a limited time.

products.name: Khazan Avatar Decoration
products.summary: Exclusive to the Kazan Quest for a limited time.

items.label: This Discord avatar decoration features a menacing, metallic circular frame composed of jagged, dark gray spikes with glowing blue crystal-like accents embedded throughout. The design gives off a sharp, armored aesthetic, reminiscent of a magical or futuristic battle-worn artifact.

products.name: Gallica Avatar Decoration
products.summary: Exclusive to Metaphor Rank Up Quest for a limited time.

items.label: A fairy is floating while flipping through pages in a book

products.name: Supply Llama
products.summary: Exclusive to the Fortnite Quest for a limited time.

items.label: A purple and blue llama body surrounds the frame, with a llama head on the top left.

products.name: Clicker Avatar Decoration
products.summary: Exclusive to The Last of Us Season 2 Quest for a limited time.

items.label: Mushroom-shaped elements in orange-red and mint green colors surround the user's avatar. The organic, flowing fungal shapes have a natural, slightly oceanic aesthetic with a hand-drawn illustration style.

products.name: Ghosts
products.summary: Look at them just spinning and grinning all day...

items.label: You notice two spooky ghosts twirling around each other in an eternal dance. Are they friend or foe?

products.name: Graveyard Cat
products.summary: Just a cat on graveyard duty.

items.label: Bathed in the glow of a full moon, a mysterious black cat is perched upon a tombstone, playfully pawing the tomb's exterior.

products.name: Jack-o’-lantern
products.summary: You can practically hear its eerie cackle...

items.label: A gleeful jack-o'-lantern cackles atop a dark, twisted branch, with bats swirling above to join in on the spooky shenanigans.

products.name: Minions
products.summary: Name a more iconic duo.

items.label: A one-eyed magic cauldron hovers in the air, bubbling with a strange, green brew. Its winged jack-o'-lantern companion flaps nearby. What mischief are they brewing?

products.name: I’m a Clown
products.summary: I opened a bunch of Loot Boxes and all I got was this stupid clown decoration. Available to use until May 2024.

items.label: An avatar wears a vibrant ensemble of colorful clown hair, bowtie, and a striking red nose that balloons and pops.

products.name: Gyoiko Sakura
products.summary: A rare blossom only seen by a fortunate few.

items.label: The petals of three lovely, green cherry blossoms drift softly across the avatar.

products.name: Mokoko
products.summary: An affectionate Mokoko wants to give you plenty of hugs! Exclusive to Mokoko Quest 2024 for a limited time.

items.label: An affectionate Mokoko hugs the avatar then slides down and climbs back up to hug the avatar again.

products.summary: Travelling at the speed of light. Available to use until 9 September 2024.

items.label: Futuristic Helmet, Blue with Green Warp Speed Light, Animated

products.summary: A sparkly crown!

items.label: A gold, sparkly crown with a llama adornment tilts up and down. The avatar sparkles and glows with a golden aura.

products.name: Freezer Bunny Lovebug
products.summary: A Sim’s coolest companion!

items.label: An adorable Freezer Bunny. It bounces upward into frame and throws hearts into the sky around the avatar.

products.name: Wingman Boba
products.summary: Your trusty VALORANT buddy, with a refreshing bubbly twist. Available to use until 6 October 2024.

items.label: VALORANT Agent Gekko's cute yellow creature presents you with a boba tea and happily floats beside your avatar, creating a delightful and playful atmosphere.
